description:
Enjoy modern living and dramatic views of Manhattan from the comfort of your own living room. 

Walk to Fort Greene Park, Downtown Brooklyn, Boerum Hill, Dumbo.  Barclays Center, BAM, Chef's Table at Brooklyn Fare, Century 21, Trader Joe's, Alamo Draft House, Pollo D'Oro, Walter's, Lulu&Po, No. 7...

A/C, 2/3, 4/5, B/F, Q/R, and G trains nearby (1 express stop to Manhattan from Dekalb & Jay St/Metro Tech Stations) 

My place is good for couples, business travelers, and families (with kids).

name: Brooklyn Penthouse *Breathtaking Manhattan Views*

photos.caption: PHENOMENAL VIEWS (AND SPACE) IN BROOKLYN. Penthouse level of luxury building in Fort Greene, BK with unobstructed view of NYC skyline and private roof terrace! Perfect for your NYC getaway.
Entrance on Fleet Place with 24 hour concierge
Large gym with modern and quality equipment, plus yoga room.
Building Interior courtyard with lounge chairs and grills
Recreational room with ping pong table, pool table and TV
Picture of interior of our unit (without our furnishings)
Private rooftop terrace with Manhattan view
Bedroom with extra comfortable Queen Mattress
